  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Anxiety Resources</h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600">Everything you need to understand, manage, and find treatment for anxiety disorders.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Introduction */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Anxiety is one of the most common mental health conditions, affecting millions of people worldwide. Whether you're experiencing generalized anxiety, panic attacks, social anxiety, or specific phobias, you're not alone—and effective treatment is available.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          This resource hub brings together everything we've published about anxiety: therapy platform reviews, evidence-based treatment information, self-help tools, and practical guides for managing symptoms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Best Resources for Anxiety */}
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Top Anxiety Resources</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/best/conditions/best-for-anxiety" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Target className="h-6 w-6 text-brand-primary mr-2" />
