          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Top-rated online therapy platforms specifically for anxiety disorders, with CBT, exposure therapy, and specialized anxiety treatment.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            View Best Platforms
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/assessments/anxiety-screening" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <CheckCircle className="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Anxiety Screening Tool</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Free, clinically-validated anxiety assessment to help you understand your symptoms and severity level.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Take Assessment
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/guides/therapy-types-explained" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <BookOpen className="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Therapy Types for Anxiety</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Learn about CBT, exposure therapy, ACT, and other evidence-based approaches for treating anxiety disorders.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Explore Therapy Types
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/worksheets/thought-record-worksheet" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <FileText className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">CBT Thought Record</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Free downloadable worksheet for identifying and challenging anxious thoughts using cognitive behavioral therapy techniques.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Download Worksheet
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/worksheets/stress-management-techniques" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Heart className="h-6 w-6 text-red-600 mr-2" />
