          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Breathing exercises, progressive muscle relaxation, and mindfulness practices for immediate anxiety relief.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            View Techniques
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/guides/crisis-resources" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <Users className="h-6 w-6 text-orange-600 mr-2" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Crisis Resources</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Immediate support hotlines and resources if you're experiencing a mental health crisis or severe anxiety attack.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />
            Get Help Now
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Understanding Anxiety */}
  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Understanding Anxiety</h2>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Anxiety disorders include generalized anxiety disorder (GAD), panic disorder, social anxiety disorder, specific phobias, and separation anxiety. While each has unique features, all involve excessive worry, fear, or nervousness that interferes with daily life.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Common Anxiety Symptoms:</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6 not-prose">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Physical Symptoms:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-blue-800">
              <li>• Rapid heartbeat or palpitations</li>
              <li>• Shortness of breath or hyperventilation</li>
              <li>• Sweating, trembling, or shaking</li>
              <li>• Muscle tension or restlessness</li>
              <li>• Fatigue or difficulty sleeping</li>
              <li>• Digestive problems</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2">Mental/Emotional Symptoms:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-purple-800">
              <li>• Excessive worry or rumination</li>
              <li>• Racing thoughts or mind going blank</li>
              <li>• Difficulty concentrating</li>
              <li>• Irritability or feeling on edge</li>
              <li>• Sense of impending danger or doom</li>
              <li>• Avoidance of anxiety-triggering situations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Evidence-Based Treatments:</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The most effective treatments for anxiety disorders include:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT):</strong> Helps identify and change anxious thought patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Exposure Therapy:</strong> Gradually facing feared situations to reduce avoidance</li>
          <li><strong>Acceptance and Commitment Therapy (ACT):</strong> Building psychological flexibility around anxiety</li>
          <li><strong>Mindfulness-Based Therapies:</strong> Learning to observe anxiety without judgment</li>
          <li><strong>Medication:</strong> SSRIs, SNRIs, or anti-anxiety medications when appropriate</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Blog Articles Coming Soon */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
